==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tessellated
<hw>Tes"sel*la`ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Formed of little squares, as mosaic work; checkered; <as>as, a
<ex>tessellated</ex> pavement</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot. & Zool.)</fld> <def>Marked like a
checkerboard; <as>as, a <ex>tessellated</ex> leaf</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tessellation</ent>⟦br⟧
